             was indicted for <rs id="t17840114-46-off248" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840114-46-off248" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840114-46-off248" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17840114-46-cd249" type="crimeDate">8th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840114-46-off248 t17840114-46-cd249"></join>, six silk handkerchiefs, value 20 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840114-46-victim488" type="victimName">
                           Charles 
                           Troutbeck
                        <interp inst="t17840114-46-victim488" type="surname" value="Troutbeck"></interp>
